title: Ullathai Allitha
subTitle: Tired of his father's disciplinarian ways and to avoid marrying a girl chosen by the latter, Raja runs away to Ooty. There, he is hired as a driver by the man whose daughter he was supposed to marry.

title: April Maadhathil
subTitle: Kathir, a poor young man, and Shweta, a rich young girl, meet in college and fall in love. However, they are unable to confess their feelings to each other.

title: Pandiya Naadu
subTitle: Sivakumar, a young man, lives in a close-knitted family. When a criminal kills his brother, he and his father decide to take revenge but in their own separate ways.

title: Bhakthi Neram
subTitle: Bhakthi Neram

title: Mundhanai Mudichu
subTitle: Mischievous Parimalam, known for pranking her villagers, falls for a widowed teacher. When he proves unyielding about not marrying her, she pulls a trick and does everything to win him over.

title: Veera
subTitle: When Muthu returns to his village, he learns that the girl he liked is dead and thus, eventually marries his employer's daughter. However, his old flame returns from the dead, leading to chaos.

title: Sivappu Sooriyan
subTitle: Vijay, a merchant navy officer, returns home to meet his sister, Selvi, and her husband, Vishwanthan. However, he finds out that they are missing and sets out to search for them.

title: Priyamanavale
subTitle: Vijay gets married to Priya at his father's behest, but on the condition that at the end of the year he will get to decide whether he wants to continue their marriage or terminate it.

title: Udhaya
subTitle: Udhaya falls in love with Vasanthi, but realises that she is already engaged. Later, when he is wrongly framed for a crime, she strives to prove his innocence.

title: Saamy
subTitle: Aarusaamy, a police officer, accepts bribes from Perumal, a gangster, in order to maintain peace in his district. However, circumstances force him to go against Perumal.

title: Chinna Gounder
subTitle: The village head is a man who sticks to honesty while making judgements. However, when he falls prey to a conspiracy, he bravely fights to ensure that justice prevails in his village.

title: Chinna Gounder

title: Coimbatore Mappillai
subTitle: When Balu moves to the city in search of career opportunities, he falls in love with Sumithra. However, Sumithra's evil cousin, Mahesh, creates a rift between their blooming love.

title: Endrendrum Kadhal
subTitle: Vijay falls in love with Meenu during a business trip and decides to marry her. However, problems arise when Meenu's brother asks him to leave India and settle in Switzerland with her family.

title: Bhakthi Neram
subTitle: Bhakthi Neram

title: Anna Nagar Mudhal Theru
subTitle: Sivaraman, a desperate unemployed youth, disguises himself as a Gorkha and takes up the job of a watchman. However, he is surprised when his childhood sweetheart moves into the colony he works in.

title: Kaalamellam Kaathiruppen
subTitle: Kannan, a man from a wealthy family, falls in love with Manimekalai, after hearing her sing in a temple, later he comes up with new ways to woo her.

title: Guna
subTitle: Guna, a mentally-disturbed man, imagines a fictitious character of a woman to be his future wife. One day, he sees a girl in a temple and assumes that she is his imaginary love and kidnaps her.

title: Viralukketha Veekkam
subTitle: Three wives are disappointed with their husbands who borrow money from people to live luxuriously. After the women get employed to earn more, their spouses start plotting against them.

title: Ayya
subTitle: Local MLA Ayya gains an opponent in Karuppusamy, the son of a corrupt MLA whom he killed in the past. Thirsty for revenge, Karuppusamy tries to create different problems for Ayya.

title: Kadhal Kottai
subTitle: Suriya finds Kamali's lost bag and mails it to her. Love blossoms between them through letters and phone calls but destiny never favours them to meet each other in person.

title: Varavu Ettana Selavu Pathana
subTitle: Sivaraman leads a happy life with his wife and children. However, things change when a rich politician moves into their neighbourhood and Sivaraman's wife tries to emulate their luxurious lifestyle.

title: Varavu Ettana Selavu Pathana
subTitle: Sivaraman leads a happy life with his wife and children. However, things change when a rich politician moves into their neighbourhood and Sivaraman's wife tries to emulate their luxurious lifestyle.

title: Vasanthakala Paravai
subTitle: Ravi, a shopkeeper, falls in love with Uma, a student, who belongs to a rich family. But their relationship is tested when Uma's brother decides to intervene and break their bond.

title: Veettoda Mappillai
subTitle: While Kandasamy's two sons-in-law are useless and unemployed, Manikkam, his third son-in-law, helps him improve his hotel business. However, the return of Kandasamy's son causes trouble.

title: Bhakthi Neram
subTitle: Bhakthi Neram

title: Pandavar Bhoomi
subTitle: Dhanasekar hires an engineer, to rebuild his ancestral house. When he falls in love with Dhanasekar's niece, Dhanasekar narrates his family's past, which changes his mind to sacrifice his love.

title: Thamizh
subTitle: Following an altercation with some dangerous goons, a man confronts a gangster and joins hands with his adversary to defeat him.

title: Samsaram Athu Minsaram
subTitle: Ammaiyappan Mudaliar fulfils every need of his four children. However, when the eldest son fights with him and leaves the house, Uma, the daughter-in-law, tries to solve their issues.

title: Vaseegara
subTitle: Bhupathi's father sends him to live under the guidance of his best friend, Viswanath, and find a job. He gets close to the family and falls in love with Viswanath's daughter, who is already engaged.

title: Thavasi
subTitle: Thavasi is a revered landlord who lives in a small village. However, his life changes drastically when a young man commits suicide due to a misjudgement he makes.

title: Surieyan
subTitle: Surieyan, an IPS officer, is accused of killing a politician. However, he goes into hiding and eventually strives to prove his innocence.

title: Rettai Jadai Vayasu
subTitle: While visiting his sister, a man falls in love with a local girl. Problems arise when the girl's mother objects to their alliance.
